        "TileImage": "$($repository af934116-44f4-47aa-9b78-933798137a32).Image",
        "Description": "This is the final Task I have for you lol all done with a Jaeger rifle and ICA ClassicBaller. If you don&apos;t have that try and use a HWK and get a loud sniper before you do this your&apos;e to stay hidden while killing all the targets. Can you get silent assassin while using loud weapons. No fiber wire this time. Tip: Try to get rid of the church men/priest and guards before going in for the kill and remember no changing clothes. This will conclude Infiltration Challenges you should get SASO loud.",
